Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:22.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,Of Cain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:28.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能重回过去.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Man Narrating]If I could just go back.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:31.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果一切能够重来,\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}If I could rub everything out,{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:34.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会从我自己开始.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}starting with myself.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:38.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,从借一件外套开始\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Starting with borrowing a jacket.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:42.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,噢,稍纵即逝的天堂\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Oh, such fleeting paradise{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:46.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,如此纯真的喜悦\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Such innocent delight{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:50.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,为了去爱\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}To love{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:53.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,被爱\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Be loved{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:58.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,摇篮曲轻唱\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}A lullaby{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:07.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,随即是一片死寂\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Then silence{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:14.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 弗朗西斯，太动听了.    - 我很荣幸，谢谢.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- [ Woman ] Frances, that was lovely.   - I'm so glad. Thank you.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:17.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[ Man ]Congratulations.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了.非常优美.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Marvelous.Most enjoyable.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,赫伯特·格林立夫.这是我的妻子,埃米莉.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Herbert Greenleaf.My wife, Emily.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:24.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.汤姆·瑞普雷.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Thank you.Tom Ripley.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:26.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗?  - 你以前在普林斯顿.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- How do you do ?  - You were at Princeton.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你很有可能认识我的儿子,迪克,迪克·格林立夫.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Most likely you'll know our son,Dick. Dickie Greenleaf.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:31.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一眼就注意到了你的外套.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Emily] I couldn't help noticing your jacket.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Yes.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:36.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,56届的.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Class of'56.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:39.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,迪克现在还好吗?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}How is Dickie ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴与见你.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Frances]We've enjoyed meeting you.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:44.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你以后能常来看看我们.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I do hope that you'll come out and see us.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:47.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢.你们实在是太好了.  -二位都很好.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Thank you. That's very kind.  - Both of you.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,-赫伯特?  -是啊,是啊.我也很希望如此.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Herbert ?  - Yes, yes. I very much hope so.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:54.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然,迪克喜欢爵士.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Of course, Dickie's idea of music is jazz.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:56.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,-噢,是吗.  -他有个萨克斯管.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Oh, dear.  - He has a saxophone.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:59.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我听来,爵士根本就是噪音.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}To my ear,jazz is just noise.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过是些靡靡之音.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Just an insolent noise.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:04.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,-很高兴见到你.  -我也一样.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Very nice to meet you.  - And you.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:06.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,-先生.  -我们在船厂见.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Sir.  - We'll see you at the shipyard.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我也很期待.  -很好.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- I hope to. - Good.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,我得赶快了!已经迟到了!\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I have to run !I'm very late !{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:17.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢,你们简直太棒了!  - 你也很棒.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Ah, you were great !  - You were great.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,令人羡慕的一对,不是吗?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Darling couple,aren't they ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:23.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊.出色的年轻人.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Yes, they are.Exceptional young man.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,-非常感谢你的外衣.  -非常感谢替我出场.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Thanks a lot for the jacket. - Thanks for filling in for me.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,小心袖口.再见,弗朗.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Take care of that wrist.Bye, Fran.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:40.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,相信我.现在买下I.B.M.股,在它崩盘之前.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Believe me.Buy I.B.M. now, before it splits.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:42.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定能大赚一笔的.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}You'll make yourself a fortune.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,你真这么认为?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}You think so ?{\c}
