Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起.对不起.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Sorry.Sorry.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Sorry.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:29.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可能也听说过迪克一直在意大利.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Mr. Greenleaf] You’ve probably heard Dickie's been living in Italy.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,蒙吉.在那不勒斯南部.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Mongibello.South of Naples.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:34.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个不知名的小地方.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}No kind of place at all.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:36.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,-早上好,先生. -弗兰克.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Good morning, sir. - Frank.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:39.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,玛吉,她的女朋友,\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Marge,his young lady,{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,好像是在写什么书.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}is supposedly writing some kind of book.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有上帝知道他到底在干吗.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}God only knows what he does.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,据说他们成天呆在沙滩和游艇上.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}By all accounts, they spend the whole time on the beach or in a sailboat.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:51.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我儿子的才能..花钱如流水.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}That's my son's talent..spending his allowance.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:54.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能否考虑去趟意大利,汤姆?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Could you ever conceive of going to Italy, Tom ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:58.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,劝我儿子回来?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Persuade my son to come home ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会付你酬劳的...\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'd pay you...{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,1000美元.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}a thousand dollars.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:10.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,是这样,我一直希望能去欧洲看看,先生,但是...\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Well, I have always wanted to go to Europe, sir, but...{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:14.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好.现在你有了去那里的理由.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Good. Now you can go for a reason.{\c}
