Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,查里帕克.我知道，是《伯德》这张专辑.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Charlie Parker.I know it. It's Bird.{\c}
