Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:59.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,-来,我来拿.  - 谢谢.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Here. I'll take it.  - Thanks.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,1000美元唾手可得.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}That thousand bucks should come in handy.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 是啊,先生.  - 我来开.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Yes, sir.  - I'll get that.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:13.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢.  - 先生,你的旅途会很愉快的.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Thank you.  - Sir. You're gonna have a great trip.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:16.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,格林立夫先生和科纳德公司老板是老友.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Mr. Greenleaf is personal friends with the Cunard people.{\c}
