Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:06.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你会说英语吗?  -请问你的名字是?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- [Ripley] Do you speak English ?  - [Man] What you name, please ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:08.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,-瑞普雷.  -跟着我吧.没问题.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Ripley.  - Follow me. No problem.{\c}
