Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,[ Italian ]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你的秘诀是什么?  -什么?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- What's your secret ?  - Excuse me ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,不，我的意思是..你是个美国人,是吗?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}No, it’s just that..You are American, aren't you ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,不,我是说--\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}No, it’s just that--{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:51.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有那么多行李,而你却,嗯,轻装上阵.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I have so much luggage,and you're so, um, streamlined.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:54.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,这,你知道,我都有点不好意思了.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}It's, you know,humiliating.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,[ Italian ]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,顺便自我介绍一下,我叫梅瑞迪斯.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'm Meredith,by the way.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:02.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好，我叫迪克.  - 梅瑞迪斯·兰德尔.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Hello, I'm Dickie.  - Meredith Randall.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:05.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,-嗯，迪克·格林立夫.  -你好.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Um, Dickie Greenleaf.  - Hello.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不是造船大亨格林立夫家的吧.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}You're not the shipping Greenleafs.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:14.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,哦,想不是来着.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Oh, trying not to be.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,想跳船来着.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Trying to jump ship.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:18.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么,嗯,他们刚刚把你的行李放错了地方吗?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}So, uh, did they put your cases in the wrong pile ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:22.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,只不过,嗯，你刚才在"R"那一栏.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}It’s just that, uh, you were in the "R" stand.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:27.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,我好像看到你在那儿了.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I thought I saw you there.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:30.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的父亲想让我回纽约.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}My father wants me back in New York.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,他造船.我宁可乘船.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}He builds boats.I'd rather sail them.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我以我母亲的姓来登记.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}So I travel under my mother's name.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:39.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你母亲叫...  -埃米莉.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Which is...  - Emily.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,开个玩笑而已.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'm just kidding.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:44.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道,很有趣的一件事,\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}You know,the funny thing is,{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是姓兰道尔.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'm not Randall either.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我姓罗吉.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'm Logue.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:53.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 是...   - 是从事纺织业的罗吉.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- As in...  - As in the textile Logues.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:56.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,想抛开这个行当.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Trying to shrug off the dress.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:58.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我也是以我母亲的姓旅游的.  -兰道尔.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- I travel under my mother's name too.  - Randall.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Right.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:03.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 那么,罗马,罗马,罗马.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Oh.  - So, Rome, Rome, Rome. - Oh.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:09.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们看起来还挺配的.再见.  -再见.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- We're partners in disguise. Bye.  - Bye.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,[ Shouting in Italian ]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:44.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,[ Driver Singing in Italian ]
