Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,伯德.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Bird.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,"这是我的脸. "\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}“This is my face. “{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:09.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,[ Italian ]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:12.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,[People Chattering in Italian]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:37.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你没还看过我新写的一章.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Woman] So I guess you didn't look at my new chapter.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会的,玛吉.我保证.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I will, Marge.I promise.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过是太热了.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}It’s just been too hot.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我今晚我为你做晚餐,你可以顺便看看.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}If I make dinner at my place tonight,maybe you could look at it then.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:56.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,迪克格林立夫?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Dickie Greenleaf?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:59.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你是?  -汤姆,汤姆·瑞普雷.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Who's that ?  - It's Tom. Tom Ripley.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆瑞普雷?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Tom Ripley ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:05.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们在普林斯顿是同学.   -是吗.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- We were at Princeton together.  - Okay.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:08.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们认识?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Did we know each other ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好.呃,我认识你,所以...\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Hello.Well, I knew you, so...{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:13.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你也该认识我.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I suppose you must have known me.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,普林斯顿是一团雾.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Princeton's like a fog.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:20.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,美国也是一团雾.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}America's like a fog.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:23.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我叫玛吉·舍伍德.汤姆...对不起,贵姓?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}This is Marge Sherwood.Tom...Sorry, what is it ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:24.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,-瑞普雷.  -你好吗?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Ripley.  - How do you do ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:28.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好,玛吉?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}How do you do, Marge ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:30.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你在蒙吉干吗?  -没什么.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- What are you doing in Mongi ?  - Nothing.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,没什么事.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Nothing much.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过是经过而已.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Just passing through.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:38.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,-经过?  -是呀.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Passing through ?  - Yeah.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可真白.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}You're so white.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:45.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,你看见过这么白的男人吗,玛吉?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Did you ever see a guy so white, Marge ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,灰色,事实上是.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Gray, actually.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像件内衣一样.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}It’s just an undercoat.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:53.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,-再说一遍?  -你知道,刚入门.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Say again ?  - You know, a primer.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,真有趣.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}That's funny.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,玛吉喜欢皮肤白的人，因为她自己就很白.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Margie likes that 'cause she's so white too.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,是呀,我是很白，而你一点也不幽默.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Yes, I do,and you're not funny.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:05.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,在你走之前请务必来和我们共进午餐.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}You should come and have lunch with us before you go.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:07.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吗,迪克?   - 当然,什么时候都可以.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Yes, Dickie ?  - Sure, anytime.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:10.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好,\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Well,{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:12.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是巧啊.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}coincidence.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:19.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一点也不记得他.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I don't remember him.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,真够搞笑的.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}That's so funny.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,希尔维那!嗨!\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Silvana ! Hey !{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我到处找你.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I've been looking all over for you.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你躲哪儿去了?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Where’ve you been hiding ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:38.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天你倒找我来了.剩下一星期都死哪儿去了?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Today you're looking for me. Where've you been the rest of the week ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:41.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,你总在工作. 来吧.上来.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}You're always working.Come on. Get on.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,和那个美国女孩在一起?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}With the American girl ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:46.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,-抓紧我.   -我恨死你了.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Hold on to me.  - I hate you.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:50.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,-啊?   -我恨死你了!\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Huh ? - I hate you!{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:54.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是连我住哪里都忘了?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Marge]Did you suddenly forget where I lived?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:56.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了.我来晚了.我是一头猪.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I know. I'm late.I'm a swine.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:58.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,-四点了.   -我刚起床.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- It's 4:00.  - I just woke up.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,-哦.  -我很抱歉.对不起.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Ohh.  - I'm sorry. I'm sorry.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 你才起床.   - 福斯托和我出去划船了.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- You just woke up.   - Fausto and I took the boat out.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:07.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们去打鱼,天才刚亮,我们什么都没捕到.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}We were fishing, and then it was dawn,and we caught absolutely nothing.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:11.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯,是吗,那好,我们没等你一起吃饭.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Mmm, yes, well,we ate everything without you.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们?   - 是啊.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- We ?  - Yes.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,-汤姆·瑞普雷来了.   -谁?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Tom Ripley's here.   - Who ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:22.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,-汤姆.你好.   -你好.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Tom. Hello.  - Hi.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:24.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你好.    -你还好吧? 我们以为你失踪了呢.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}-Hello.   -How are you? Thought you'd disappeared.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:27.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们都想派个搜索队去找你了.   -没有.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- We were gonna send out a search party.  - No.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:31.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,-没有,还在这儿呢.   -汤姆在和我谈论他的旅途.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- No, still here.  - Tom was telling me about his journey.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:35.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我笑得鼻血都要喷出来了.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Giggling] Made me laugh so hard I almost got a nosebleed.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:39.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 那不是很爽?   - 闭嘴.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Is that good ?  - Shut up.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:42.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉.我很抱歉.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry.I'm sorry.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:45.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是很可耻.不过我爱你.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'm despicable.But I love you.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:48.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你爱我吗?你爱我吗?    -我煞风景了.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Do you love me ? Do you love me ?  - I'm intruding.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:50.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能替我调杯马提尼酒?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Can you mix a martini ?{\c}
