Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:07.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都应该有一样才能.你的是什么?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Everybody should have one talent. What's yours ?{\c}
