Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你从什么时候开始唱的.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'll tell you when to join the chorus.{\c}
