Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我遇到了一个普林斯顿的同学,\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Dickie] I bumped into an old friend from Princeton,{\c}
