Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:17.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说他会一直缠着我直到我同意...\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}He says he's going to haunt me until I agree...{\c}
