Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.29,0:37:26.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,[Whistle Blows]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.59,0:37:34.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我对她来说还有意义\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}If I meant anything to her{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.62,0:37:39.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会勇敢,我将会对她唱这首歌\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'd be brave, and here’s the song I'd bring to her{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.47,0:37:42.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会对她唱道\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'd sing to her{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.26,0:37:46.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许我是唯一一个\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}May I be the only one{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.48,0:37:48.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,对她说\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}To say I{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.03,0:37:53.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我第一次见到你的时候\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Really fell in love the day I{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.36,0:37:56.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就深深地爱上了你\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}First set eyes on you{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.12,0:38:02.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我能否   -你在干吗?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}-  May I  - What are you doing ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.58,0:38:05.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,哦.我只是在自娱自乐罢了.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Oh. I was just amusing myself.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.54,0:38:10.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,-对不起.   -我希望你能脱下我的衣服.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Sorry. - I wish you'd get out of my clothes.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.96,0:38:15.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你是不是还穿了我的鞋?  -你说过我可以先穿你的外套...\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Do you have my shoes on too ? - You said I could pick out a jacket...{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.60,0:38:20.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能回你自己的房间脱?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Did you get undressed in your own room ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.43,0:38:25.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你错过了火车.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Thought you missed the train.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.77,0:38:28.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪用车带我回来的.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Freddie drove me back in his car.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.44,0:38:31.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,-弗雷迪也来了吗?   -他就在楼下.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Is Freddie here ? - He's downstairs.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.53,0:38:34.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚只是在瞎胡闹。\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I was just fooling around.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.74,0:38:38.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,别再说了.我刚刚只是在瞎胡闹.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Don't say anything.I was just fooling around.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.45,0:38:42.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Sorry.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.37,0:38:46.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,天.在意大利就一件灯芯绒外套.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Freddie]God. A corduroy jacket in Italy.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.88,0:38:48.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,-早上好,汤姆.   -早上好.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- [Marge] Good morning, Tom.  - Morning.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.88,0:38:51.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,-来一起坐.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- [ Chuckles ]- Come join us.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.51,0:38:57.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗨.我也想要你这份工作,汤米.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Hey. I want this job of yours, Tommy.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.59,0:39:00.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚还在说,你住在意大利,\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I was just saying,you live in Italy,{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.60,0:39:04.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你住的是迪克的,你吃的是迪克的,\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}you stay at Dickie's house,you eat Dickie's food,{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.69,0:39:09.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你穿的是他的,他父亲还得给你付帐.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}you wear his clothes,and his father picks up the tab.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.15,0:39:12.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想干了,\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Chuckles]If you get bored,{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.69,0:39:16.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我,我来做.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}you let me know, 'cause I'll do it.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.39,0:39:19.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我来做.-潜到底!\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- I'll do it.  - [Dickie] To the mainland!{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.16,0:39:26.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你真应该下来.太棒了.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}You really should go in.It's marvelous.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.46,0:39:29.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很好.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I'm fine.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.62,0:39:31.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,[ Dickie Shouting ]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.14,0:39:41.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Are you okay ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.65,0:39:44.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Sure.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.48,0:39:51.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,和迪克一起是这样的...\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}The thing with Dickie...{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.32,0:39:56.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像是阳光为你闪耀,金光灿烂.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}It's like the sun shines on you, and it's glorious.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.78,0:40:01.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果他遗忘了你，就会寒彻骨.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}And then he forgets you and it's very, very cold.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.41,0:40:03.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我正在学会适应.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}So I'm learning.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.41,0:40:06.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,当他注意你时,你会感觉整个世界只属于你一人.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}When you have his attention, you feel you're the only person in the world.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.00,0:40:09.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么人人都爱他.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}That's why everybody loves him.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.79,0:40:13.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,总是这样.每当一个人进入他的生活...\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}It's always the same. Whenever someone new comes into his life...{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.50,0:40:16.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,弗雷迪,福斯托,彼得 史密斯-金斯利.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Freddie, Fausto,Peter Smith-Kingsley.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.57,0:40:18.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是个大好人.你见过他吗?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}He's wonderful.Have you met him ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.05,0:40:23.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,特别是你.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Especially you.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.02,0:40:30.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,这还只是男孩子.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}And that’s just the boys.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.85,0:40:37.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,[ Dickie,Freddie Shouting ]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.99,0:40:41.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,快来抓他!快来抓他!\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Come get him !Come get him !{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.82,0:40:43.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我,为什么每次男人在一起玩闹,\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Tell me, why is itthat when men play,{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.84,0:40:45.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们总是完一些杀来杀去的游戏?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}they always play at killing each other ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.95,0:40:49.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,他想淹死我!他想淹死我!\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Dickie] He's drowning me!He's drowning me!{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.04,0:40:57.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,-关于科尔蒂纳的是我很抱歉,顺便说一句. -科尔蒂纳怎么了?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- I'm sorry about Cortina, by the way. - What about Cortina ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.38,0:41:01.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,他还没...迪克还没告诉过你吗?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Didn't...Didn't-Didn't Dick say ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.97,0:41:04.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,他对弗雷迪说过,然而-然而明显他还没有...\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[Sighs] He spoke to Freddie,and-and apparently...{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.97,0:41:06.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是行不通的.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}it's not going to work out.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.68,0:41:11.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是因为其他所有人都会滑雪,\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}It's because everyone else can ski,{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.29,0:41:13.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不会自然会产生些影响, \N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}and it affects where you stay,{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.90,0:41:23.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,来吧,弗雷迪.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}[ Dickie ]Come on, Freddie.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.45,0:41:26.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,至少留下来过圣母节.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}At least stick around for the Festival of the Madonna.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.12,0:41:28.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,-全镇的人都会出来..  -我不这样想.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- The whole town comes out..  - I don’t think so.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.79,0:41:33.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我自己在罗马,嗯,有个圣母节.你不如和我一起来?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}I have my own, uh, Madonna back in Rome.Why don’t you come back with me ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.54,0:41:36.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,狂多的女人.噢.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}A lot of ladies.Ooh.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.12,0:41:38.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,[ Chuckles ]
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.72,0:41:43.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,-噢,天.  -你来掌舵?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}- Oh, God. - You want to take over ?{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.97,0:41:45.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的,没问题.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Yeah, sure.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.97,0:41:48.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,就对着卡普里的方向就行了.绕过岩石.\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Just point her at Capri.Avoid the rocks.{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.97,0:41:51.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿?\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\c&H00ffff&\3c&H000000&}Where are you going ?{\c}
